-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 14, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mdg1665702961567.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mdg1665702961567.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mdg1665702961567.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mdg1665702961567\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      map fixed length to variable\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Map fields with a fixed length storage format (CHAR) to a variable length storage format.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"mdg1665702961567__topic_d57638e1_d57639e1_d57640e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mdg1665702961567__p_d57641e1_d57642e1_d57643e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$PGS_PARAMS</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n                              map fixed length to variable\n                              <code class=\"ph codeph\">:on</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">off</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mdg1665702961567__p_d57644e1_d57645e1_d57646e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$PGS_PARAMS</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">= fv:on</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">off</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mdg1665702961567__section_oyj_d45_jcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d659576e81\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mdg1665702961567__p_d57653e1_d57654e1_d57655e1\">If the setting is not specified, it defaults to\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">off</code>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mdg1665702961567__p_d57656e1_d57657e1_d57658e1\">This setting can greatly reduce the disk space\n            required for large table sets. However, it may also reduce the database performance by\n            20%-50%.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pau1665702961889.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Data Packing for PostgreSQL</a><p>Uniface packing codes are mapped to PostgreSQL storage formats (data types).</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529862\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529862\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "map fixed length to variable Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 14, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 map fixed length to variable Map fields with a fixed length storage format (CHAR) to a variable length storage format. USYS$PGS_PARAMS = map fixed length to variable :on | off USYS$PGS_PARAMS = fv:on | off Description If the setting is not specified, it defaults to off . This setting can greatly reduce the disk space required for large table sets. However, it may also reduce the database performance by 20%-50%. Related Links Data Packing for PostgreSQL Uniface packing codes are mapped to PostgreSQL storage formats (data types). Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}